hb.math.graph
Class Sepset

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--hb.math.graph.Edge
        |
        +--hb.math.graph.Sepset
public class Sepset
extends Edge
implements java.util.Collection, java.lang.Comparable

A sepset of vertices is a set of vertices that seperates two specified clusters, X and Y. The vertices in a sepset is exactly those that can be found in both clusters, i.e. X intersect Y.

See Also:
Cluster, Vertex
